While trying to earn money at the country club, Bart acquires 
Denis Leary's cell phone after Leary angrily chucks it away. 
Bart keeps the phone and makes prank calls pretending to be 
Leary and when Marge finds out what Bart is doing she contacts 
Leary. Denis says Bart might as well keep the phone, but he 
advises her to activate the GPS system in the phone so she 
can track Bart's every move.
